Lisa Brenner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_Brenner 0 Lisa Brenner (born Lisa Dawn Goldstein; February 12, 1974) is an American actress. Brenner played Maggie Cory on Another World. She was also in All My Children as Allison Sloan. Lisa_Brenner ( born Lisa_Dawn_Goldstein ; February_12_,_1974 ) is an_American_actress . Brenner played Maggie_Cory on Another_World . She was also in All_My_Children as Allison_Sloan .
